reviewText: At times interesting, other times silly. Lots of four-letter words spoken in English, especially by the evil android. Not for families.

Long lost magic in Hollywood movies can be found in this drama. Its a story about love larger than life. A scientist who predicts his own death in order to protect his beloved one from an approaching danger uses his knowledge to send an android from the future to the present times. The enemy takes form of 11 different androids. The drama is very well directed. Amazing fight scenes are  accompanied by original and memorable soundtrack.
